00:16:16.140 --> 00:16:17.460
Gracias, Alteza.

00:16:28.740 --> 00:16:29.580
Chu Yu,

00:16:31.740 --> 00:16:32.660
La vida es corta

00:16:33.380 --> 00:16:34.380
y fugaz.

